{
  "name": "SlicerItem",
  "summary": "<p>若要访问表示切片器中当前选中的按钮的 <strong>SlicerItem</strong> 对象，请使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Slicer\">Slicer</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.ActiveItem\">ActiveItem</a></strong> 属性。如果切片器筛选数据透视表，那么若要访问表示该切片器中所有项目的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItems/SlicerItems .htm#SlicerItems.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 集合，请使用与该 <strong>Slicer</strong> 对象关联的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 属性。如果切片器筛选 OLAP 层次结构级别，那么若要访问表示该切片器中项目的 <strong>SlicerItems</strong> 集合，请使用表示该层次结构级别的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerItems\">SlicerItems</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_id”的切片器缓存中所有切片器项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存中第二个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示切片器中的一个项目。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Caption",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项的标签文本。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_date”的切片器缓存中第一项的标签文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Caption</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上数据透视表第一个切片器的缓存中切片器项的标签文本逐个赋值到单元格中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItems = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = sliItems.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Caption</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HasData",
      "summary": "<p>如果切片器项中包含与当前手动筛选状态相符的数据，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n<p>此属性只在启用了交叉筛选的情况下才受支持，否则将生成运行时错误。若要确定是否为与数据透视表关联的切片器启用了交叉筛选，请检查指定的 <strong>SlicerItem</strong> 对象的父 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.CrossFilterType\">CrossFilterType</a></strong> 属性值。若要确定是否为与 OLAP 数据源关联的切片器启用了交叉筛选，请检查对应于被筛选的 OLAP 层次结构的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.SlicerCacheLevel\">SlicerCacheLevel</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCacheLevel/SlicerCacheLevel .htm#SlicerCacheLevel.CrossFilterType\">CrossFilterType</a></strong> 属性值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项是否包含与当前手动筛选状态相符的数据。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿第二个切片器缓存中第二个切片器项是否包含与当前手动筛选状态相符的数据。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasData</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存中名为“张五”的切片器项是否包含与当前手动筛选状态相符的数据。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;张五&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasData</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项的名称。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_date”的切片器缓存中第三个切片器项的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张数据透视表的第一个切片器的缓存中第四个切片器项的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerItems</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第四个切片器项的名称：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sliItem.Name}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项的父 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerCache/SlicerCache .htm#SlicerCache.SlicerCache\">SlicerCache</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "SlicerCache",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Selected",
      "summary": "<p>如果选择了切片器项，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置是否选择了切片器项。连接到非 OLAP 数据源的切片器，可读/写。连接到 OLAP 数据源的切片器，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中活动工作簿上第二个切片器缓存中第一个切片器项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上数据透视表第一个切片器的缓存中名为“张三”的切片器项是否被选中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;张三&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SourceName",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项的源名称。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_score”的切片器缓存中第六个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_score&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张数据透视表的第一个切片器的缓存中第二个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SourceNameStandard",
      "summary": "<p>当切片器项有本地化版本且其 <strong>SourceNameStandard</strong> 属性值不同于 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItem/SlicerItem .htm#SlicerItem.SourceName\">SourceName</a></strong> 属性值时，将使用此属性，例如对于日期格式。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回以标准英语（美国）格式设置表示的切片器项的源名称。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示以标准英语（美国）格式表示的第一张工作簿上名为“切片器_date”的切片器缓存中第一个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_date&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceNameStandard</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示以标准英语（美国）格式表示的活动工作表上数据透视表的第一个切片器的缓存的第一个切片器项的源名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sliItem.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceNameStandard</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回切片器项的值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上名为“切片器_name”的切片器缓存中第三个切片器项的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;切片器_name&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上数据透视表的第一个切片器的缓存中第五个切片器项的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sliItem = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SlicerCache</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerItems</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第五个切片器项的值：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sliItem.Value}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}